title: Eiza González 🤣
description:
Eiza González (I Care a Lot, Godzilla vs. Kong) talks to Justin about breaking into acting in the U.S., they talk about their time spent volunteering with This Is About Humanity in Tijuana, and Eiza shares why she has a hatred for The Muppets.
